0.3.name: wordpress/mylco
0.3.description:
Now you can maintain and verify the state of the backlinks on the linking pages from your link-exchange-partners.

Translators

I hope to find some kind people who will translate the plugin in other languages too.

In addition, I would like to thank Jürgen Mayer for making the banner of this plugin.
